lead_paragraph: DeMar DeRozan won a shootout with Russell Westbrook, scoring 37 points to lead the Toronto Raptors to a 112-102 victory over the Oklahoma City Thunder on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: DeRozan Scores 37, Leads Raptors Past Thunder 112-102
